# Setup Notes

## API Keys and Configuration

This application requires an OpenAI API key to function. Follow these steps to set up your environment:

1. Create an account on [OpenAI](https://platform.openai.com/) if you don't already have one
2. Generate an API key from your OpenAI dashboard
3. Create a file named `.env` in the root directory of this project
4. Add your API key to the `.env` file in this format:
